Name: Fairytale Lullaby Mount
Desc:
[Master Level: 1]
Travel by riding a Fairytale Lullaby mount, which enables High Altitude Flight, to travel very fast.

Desc.Old:
[Master Level: 1]
Ride on the Fairytale Lullaby Mount that can double-jump to travel very fast. Double-click a location on the World Map and you will automatically fly to the destination by following the navigation. (Auto flight is only available on certain continents, such as Victoria Island. You can expand your Smart Riding Authorization Continents by purchasing Flight Permits from Instructor Irvin.)
